cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision techniques for detecting carried objects from a single video frame. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for feature extraction and matching, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image processing techniques, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper's focus on detecting carried objects could suggest that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics).
